Tga '''Roma''' tamdint tamaẓunt n [[Ṭalyan|Ṭṭalyan]] zɣ 1871. Tg ula tamdint lli akkʷ imqqurn ɣ tsga n Lazyu, s tsga tarakalt n Latyum. Tettubna iggi n wasif n Tibr, zdɣn gis kra n 2.8 id mlyun n umzdaɣ, yan usiḍn n OECD ar ittini mas d wuṭṭun n imzdaɣ n tsgiwin n tmdint ar ilkkm s 3.47 id mlyun.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20070614043229/http://213.253.134.43/oecd/pdfs/browseit/0406041E.PDF "Competitive Cities in the Global Economy"] [PDF]</ref> Lliɣ tsul tga talimbṛaṭurt n Roma tamaynut, ar aqqran i Roma s ''Tamdint lli ur ittmttatn'' acku tkka tt inn yad ɣ akud ann tga taqburt. Tkka 357 n usggʷas tga tamaẓunt n tmnkda tarumiyt. 

Tettyussan bahra Roma acku tga tgmmi n Tmẓẓalut Takatulikt, ula anssixf nns, walli mu ttinin Lbaba. Izdɣ ɣ tmdint n Vatikan lli igan yat tgzzumt ɣ iẓẓlmḍ-agmuḍan n tmdint n Roma 

